{"id":"api/core/afterRender","title":"afterRender","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/afterRender\", \"name\": \"afterRender\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/render3/after_render_hooks.ts#L169-L248\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"afterrender\">afterRender<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/afterRender#afterrender\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label dev-preview\" title=\"此 API 仅供开发者预览\">\n      <a href=\"guide/releases#developer-preview\">开发者预览</a>\n    </label>\n    \n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5m9az62bizc1zvfglfogg9f1q\">注册一个回调，每次应用程序完成渲染时都会调用。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/afterRender#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/core/afterRender\" class=\"code-anchor\">afterRender</a></span>(callback: VoidFunction, options?: <a href=\"api/core/AfterRenderOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterRenderOptions</a>): <a href=\"api/core/AfterRenderRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterRenderRef</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">参数</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e1u07soqllrwux3on5v3eoiwl\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>callback</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>VoidFunction</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bvj8n0bajxlz4j5kebhjv2b62\">要注册的回调函数</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bctpqv6pe3qufag0kdnkhac2q\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>options</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/core/AfterRenderOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterRenderOptions</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p>可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/core/AfterRenderRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterRenderRef</a></code></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/afterRender#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <div class=\"alert is-critical\">\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8rajwjshpimd1zi01wx7p7oa4\">您应该始终明确指定非默认的\n<a href=\"api/core/AfterRenderPhase\">阶段</a>，否则可能会导致严重的性能下降。</p>\n</div>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c6jzbu6g7vfibi5a7o0taatfj\">请注意，回调函数将按注册顺序执行</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8fe81e0wh59nkiq7usqe93yp2\">仅在浏览器平台上</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8sxratv17x5m8kzukkhsr1k0a\">每次渲染一次</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7f8lq68nc9c8c7wp60k4n8xya\">仅在浏览器平台上</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"alert is-important\">\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bm05qavjycvbx1h8vycrcvd13\">组件在回调运行之前不能保证已经\n<a href=\"guide/hydration\">水合</a>。 直接读取或写入 DOM 和布局时必须小心。</p>\n</div>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"epmq5ahrerfrrnlvk4ncvcs8f\">更多信息请参阅\n<a href=\"api/core/afterRender#usage-notes\">使用注意...</a></p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/afterRender#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7f5pxb8y7ijgk3s4552pebvg\">使用\n<code><a href=\"api/core/afterRender\" class=\"code-anchor\">afterRender</a></code>来在每次渲染后读取或写入 DOM。</p>\n<h3 id=\"example\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"lzz2v4ucg07faxnpe2bu1wa1\">范例<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/afterRender#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'my-cmp',\n  template: `&lt;span #content&gt;{{ ... }}&lt;/span&gt;`,\n})\nexport class MyComponent {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>('content') contentRef: <a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a>;\n\n  constructor() {\n    <a href=\"api/core/afterRender\" class=\"code-anchor\">afterRender</a>(() =&gt; {\n      console.log('content height: ' + this.contentRef.nativeElement.scrollHeight);\n    }, {phase: <a href=\"api/core/AfterRenderPhase#Read\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterRenderPhase.Read</a>});\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/AfterRenderOptions\n - api/core/AfterRenderPhase\n - errors/NG0602\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n - guide/ssr\n - guide/update-to-version-17\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/AfterRenderOptions\n - api/core/AfterRenderPhase\n - api/core/AfterRenderPhase#Read\n - api/core/AfterRenderRef\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/ElementRef\n - api/core/ViewChild\n - api/core/afterRender#afterrender\n - api/core/afterRender#description\n - api/core/afterRender#example\n - api/core/afterRender#usage-notes\n - guide/hydration\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/render3/after_render_hooks.ts#L169-L248\n-->"}